getSearchResults

public java.util.List<EntityIdentifier> getSearchResults()
Get the list of found entities.

Returns:
List of entities found by the last search; this can be: - null, meaning no search has been performed, or search was cleared. - an empty collection, meaning search was performed but did not return anything. - a non empty collection, meaning search results are available.
